      _TV Show Notes_ 
      ===============----------------------------------------------------
       
         Susie the parrot is in a petulant mood as she faces a move 
         to a sanctuary, and a colony of penguins trapped by an oil 
         spill return to the water. Presented by Michaela Strachan 
         and Matt Baker

